Taxi in Riga is specially for Riga, Latvia designed free iPhone application, which can be used to call for taxi and also to find the cheapest taxi company available.


MAIN FEATURES:

30+ in Riga, Latvia working taxi companies;
Special discounts may appear from time to time;
Detailed prices;
Immediate calls from application;
MurTT taxi company ratings;
Favorites list;
Price comparison for average (~8km) route;
Current location and address finder;
Automatically updated rates, ratings, discounts and list of companies.
